Package: matrispace.app
Title: MatriSpace - Offline Spatial Transcriptomics Matrisome Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("MatriSpace", "Team", email = "matrisomeproject@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: An offline, upload-only version of MatriSpace for analysing spatial
    transcriptomics data with focus on matrisome (extracellular matrix) gene analysis.
    Users upload their own Seurat or SpatialExperiment .rds files. All matrisome
    reference data ships bundled with the package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
